This is the finalized **Technical Specification Document (TSD)** for your global freelance and rewards platform. It is organized using the **TLS (Three-Layer System)** architecture to ensure every feature has a designated place for professional development.

---
## 1. Professional Page Plan

### A. The Public Facing Site (Landing & Trust)
* **Home Page:** Hero section with CTA, "How it Works" guide, and platform statistics.
* **Leaderboard:** Live rankings of top earners and referrers to drive competition.
* **Proof of Payment Wall:** A public feed of recent payouts (censored) to build global credibility.
* **Services/Features:** Detailed breakdown of Ad-watching, Video tasks, and the Spin-to-Earn system.
* **FAQ & Help Center:** Clear documentation on payment cycles and account rules.
* **Legal/Compliance:** Terms of Service and Privacy Policy (GDPR/CCPA compliant).

### B. User Portal (The Earner’s Dashboard)
* **Main Dashboard:** Real-time earnings snapshot and daily task progress.
* **The Earning Hub:**
    * **Ad-Watch & Video Lounge:** High-performance interfaces for YouTube/TikTok embeds.
    * **Lucky Spin Room:** Gamified UI with anti-cheat button verification.
* **Referral Management:** * Unique link generator.
    * **Multi-Level Tree:** Visual breakdown of Level 1, 2, and 3 downlines.
* **Membership Tier Center:** Upgrade options (Basic/Gold/Platinum) to increase earning limits.
* **Wallet & Payouts:** Transaction history and withdrawal requests (Fiat/Crypto).
* **Profile & Security:** 2FA setup, KYC document upload, and language/currency settings.

### C. Admin Portal (The Command Center)
* **Main Analytics:** Global KPIs—total users, site-wide revenue vs. payout liability.
* **User & KYC Management:** Verification queue and user ban/unban tools.
* **Content & Ad Manager:** * Ad/Video uploader with "per-view" pricing and daily caps.
    * Spin Controller (odds management).
* **Financial Manager:** * **Withdrawal Queue:** Manual/Batch approval of payouts.
    * **Kill-Switch:** Emergency button to pause all site financial activities.
* **Security Monitor:** Real-time flags for IP/Device conflicts (Multi-account detection).

